計劃"},{"pid":"04a485e718bcb8f0752bcd8b5d1d2ce90f229d7b","tid":1081192,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:46:10.000Z","msg":"如果有人捐完而自己屋企人不幸需要肝臟<br />\n<br />\n已經捐過係唔可以再捐,到時自己屋企人就等死<br />\n呢4大自私蝗蟲一定唔會捐肝救你"},{"pid":"7bac489f4bdf8ea67e9e6fadff3fbf0657989bb9","tid":1081192,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"問豬肉檔"},{"pid":"fb0fd56ddae74bf547e7b2bd87bc950424f4697a","tid":1081192,"uid":31575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:58:45.000Z","msg":"好媽媽唔比自己仔女承受風險，好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家都可以學呢位孝順媽媽咁，唔好做任何有風險既事令自己媽媽擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b95766eaab42bc93d2f2794c541a41cb40e307","tid":1081192,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"有圈中人講事主係bno香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6394fe5845f0e11488706003be2aa108445c5328","tid":1081192,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:09:30.000Z","msg":"毒果你之前唔係咁報導喎，比人屌到要講真話呀，毒果執撚左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}